+## Architecture
+
+```
+  Phone / Browser
+       |
+       |  (pair + observe + control)
+       v
+  apps/zend-home-gateway/index.html   ← command center (HTML, no build step)
+       |
+       |  HTTP REST
+       v
+  services/home-miner-daemon/         ← daemon (Python stdlib only)
+       |
